							<p><em>Aradiani - Public Relations Officer</em>
							<br>In charge of promoting Invictvs to members of the EverQuest community. Develops and maintains the guild webpage. 
							
							<p><em>Falloraan - Public Relations Officer</em>
							<br>In charge of promoting Invictvs to members of the EverQuest community. Develops and maintains the guild webpage. 
						</blockquote>
